{"tid":2334691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【防疫抗疫基金4.0】立法會通過注資64億元　工聯會投下棄權票","createTime":"2020-12-21T10:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T10:49:40.000Z","uid":271829,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ad8e8f3eb96b26de0fa05623a8648d2c79b1ed4c","tid":2334691,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T10:24:09.000Z","msg":"立法會財務委員會今日通過，向防疫抗疫基金注資64億元。經過7小時的審議，最終以32票贊成、1票反對、3票棄權獲得通過，投下棄權票的為工聯會。<br />\n<br />\n投下反對票的熱血公民鄭松泰指出，64億元是遠遠不足，有個別行業在過去4輪的基金中所得的支援都是不足，正面對衰退的情況。他擔心，個別行業的專業人員，流失後是不能挽回的局面，例如文化界、舞蹈界等。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會麥美娟則解釋，明白基金對關閉處所的支援重要，但政府推出前卻沒有諮詢工會及業界，而且市民已經生活於水深火熱之中，看不到64億元能幫到大忙，亦看不到政府的措施能有效控制疫情，直言港府不能忘記打工仔，應該要有具針對性措施，協助不同行業的從員，改善他們的生活，亦要改善防疫措施，直指疫情一天不「清零」，香港的庫房會因不斷推出基金而「清零」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2830000/2834076/IMG-20201221-WA0009_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2830000%2F2834076%2FIMG-20201221-WA0009_600.jpg&h=43840ddc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 立法會通過第四輪防疫抗疫基金。（馮漢柱攝）"},{"pid":"16a92b6556a6e97f039e7048f789fb2949d5c90a","tid":2334691,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T10:27:06.000Z","msg":"土共真係養唔熟<br />\n兔死狗烹係遲早嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8f8caed6d4598d40a3b396e05722ba7322ac3c","tid":2334691,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T10:28:40.000Z","msg":"反對泰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac3eb8794f5b3bfa04b6604cbe2e6b42878c4a4","tid":2334691,"uid":73586,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T10:29:08.000Z","msg":"唔支持但唔反對"},{"pid":"aad32f464d9b18491e18adc577353c500e221c49","tid":2334691,"uid":10503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T10:29:31.000Z","msg":"忠誠反對派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f67196123f7de99b3de9c8b43b5007233d516c13","tid":2334691,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T10:30:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc82f97bb3b9badc432494ece382eebb45e4c9d","tid":2334691,"uid":99962,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T10:34:03.000Z","msg":"松泰呢d咪叫做到野囉"},{"pid":"7c8b84fbf160be811aa324a21e5e34664b39e541","tid":2334691,"uid":353587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T10:44:13.000Z","msg":"工聯會果然別樹一格 既不支持 又唔反對<br />\n做「忠誠棄權派」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c832c4e55ff103353b7779fdde6114da832d3bc","tid":2334691,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"7c8b84fbf160be811aa324a21e5e34664b39e541","tid":2334691,"uid":353587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T10:44:13.000Z","msg":"工聯會果然別樹一格 既不支持 又唔反對<br />\n做「忠誠棄權派」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T10:49:40.000Z","msg":"工聯會 變左 民主黨 替工<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_combo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/104469819_P8qUi_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F104469819_P8qUi_1200x0.png&h=5228a788&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}